<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span><span class="c2">(٧٤)</span> ... <span class="c3">{قُرَّةَ أَعْيُنٍ}</span> ... تَقَرُّ بِهِمْ عُيُونُنَا، وَبِهِمْ نَانَسُ وَنَفْرَحُ.<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span><span class="c2">(٧٤)</span> ... <span class="c3">{إِمَامًا}</span> ... قُدْوَةً يُقْتَدَى بِه فِي الخَيْرِ.<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span><span class="c2">(٧٥)</span> ... <span class="c3">{الْغُرْفَةَ}</span> ... أَعْلَى مَنَازِلِ الجَنَّةِ.<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span><span class="c2">(٧٥)</span> ... <span class="c3">{وَسَلَامًا}</span> ... تَسْلِيمًا مِنَ المَلَائِكَةِ، وَسَلَامَةً مِنَ الآفَاتِ.<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span><span class="c2">(٧٧)</span> ... <span class="c3">{مَا يَعْبَأُ}</span> ... مَا يَكْتَرِثُ بِكُمْ وَلَا يُبَالِي.<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span><span class="c2">(٧٧)</span> ... <span class="c3">{دُعَاؤُكُمْ}</span> ... عِبَادَتُكُمْ وَسُؤَالُكُمْ إِيَّاهُ.<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span><span class="c2">(٧٧)</span> ... <span class="c3">{لِزَامًا}</span> ... عَذَابًا مُلَازِمًا لَكُمْ.<a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>